{"title": "Ultimate Salient", "description": "As an author of Science Fiction stories, Eben Clinton is approached to send a critical message into the future to a specific person, Brian O'Shea, who will not be born for another two years! Eben takes on the challenge to write a story that will survive the intervening time before Brian needs the message it contains. Explore the timeless concepts of struggles against oppression, sacrifice and the quest for freedom that is the story Brian needs to read.... (Summary by Cyndajm)", "duration": 8947, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "9804", "name": "Nelson S. Bond"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/theultimatesalient_2603_librivox/ultimatesalient_2603.jpg", "copyright_year": "1940", "genres": ["Science Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "cyndajm"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "cyndajm"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Christine Rottger"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Christine Rottger"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "I", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/theultimatesalient_2603_librivox/ultimatesalient_01_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 997}, {"section": 2, "title": "II", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/theultimatesalient_2603_librivox/ultimatesalient_02_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1213}, {"section": 3, "title": "III", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/theultimatesalient_2603_librivox/ultimatesalient_03_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1050}, {"section": 4, "title": "IV", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/theultimatesalient_2603_librivox/ultimatesalient_04_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1037}, {"section": 5, "title": "V", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/theultimatesalient_2603_librivox/ultimatesalient_05_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1609}, {"section": 6, "title": "VI", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/downlo